snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Private Idol Disc Vol 02 - Uchiyama Miki (1996)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Private Idol Disc Vol. 2: Uchiyama Miki is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Sada Soft, which was released in Japan in 1996.
